metadata.name: Bring me sunshines
metadata.description:
"Dear, bring me not red roses,
but a bunch of sunflowers
And paint all my blues 
with those yellows."

This painting represents those testing dark times in our lives when all we need is a little happiness and light. Sunflowers and the colour yellow represents happiness and sunshine whereas blue as a colour and as a word is defined by the state of melancholy and depression.
